			<h3>Avoid close contact</h3>
			<small>Posted by Meng on Mar.6 </small>
			<p>
				<li>Avoid close contact (within 6 inches) with people who are sick</li>
				<li>Put distance between yourself and other people if COVID-19 is spreading in your community. </li>
			</p>
